                            <comment id="14408637" author="cziegeler" created="Fri, 26 Aug 2005 06:16:51 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Retesting today without updated from the Maven svn, the NPE does not appear anymore (I guess this is due to some updates of some dependency snapshots for the compiler?). So specifying &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;1.3.02&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; or the ranges works! So I can use this as a workaround.&lt;br/&gt;
So the only open issue is that the version specified in the POM is not used.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
